column5: I'am only 56 Thats right ! ..... and i lost 150 pounds in just one weekend . Yes !  i did it by not fishing and by winterizing the boat and by getting a new invoicing program for the first time ever up and running for my buisness . It was'nt easy but i was determand to stay at it and i did , Wow! i never knew i could feel this good . Now i can smile with confidents , plus it makes feel like unwinterizing the boat and having fun again .
Winterize the boat every Saturday. In two short weeks you'll be gone.
Funny, I was thinking the same thing,
More than likely on of his kids finally left home !!!!!!!   vance
Congrats. You've been able to do in 2 days what most people can't even do in 2 years
Ha ha ha.. I was gonna say that...
.... more about the relief that comes when you except new technology that makes your every day life easyer .
